(avoid adding personal details, provide github handle(preferred) or first name and last name) @Jacquesattaque Marlena Spidalieri What's the expected date of this change to deploy on Shopify? As soon as possible.

issue.body:
## Why are you adding this icons?
I'm adding/updating this icon because we are publishing the Underpay payment gateway app for review and distribution.

#### Help us identify yourself
- [x] I'm associated with the brand and I've read all the brand icon’s guidelines.

- [x] All icons have a corresponding entry in `db/payment_icons.yml`
- [x] I have followed the icon guidelines detailed in the [CONTRIBUTING.md](https://github.com/activemerchant/payment_icons/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) file

#### If the icons are intended for use by Shopify, please provide the following info:
Who are you working with at Shopify? Payment Partner Account ID: 3007420

What's the expected date of this change to deploy on Shopify? App adding the Underpay payment method submitted for approval
